# Blocking Only (P20)

**Never background tasks.** Run everything in blocking manner.

- No `--bg` flag
- No spawn-and-return
- Agent waits for completion
- Runner restart commands: always blocking (no --bg)

Runner: `cargo run -p runner -- restart-od` (blocks until process exits). Never `restart-od --bg`.
